          "mount": "turret",
          "linked": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Listening Post",
      "desc": "Intelligence-gathering station disguised as a civilian weather monitoring platform. Her sensor arrays are ten times more powerful than her cover story requires, and her crew of twelve includes eight intelligence analysts, two communications specialists, a cook, and a security officer whose official title is 'maintenance technician.' She monitors military communications, tracks ship movements, and compiles reports that shape the strategic decisions of governments. Officially, she doesn't exist. Unofficially, everyone knows she's there and pretends not to.",
      "notes": "Intelligence gathering. Disguised as civilian platform. Small crew. Classified.",
      "size": 8,
      "loco": "none",
      "toughLevel": -1,
      "armourLevel": 0,
      "speedLevel": 0,
      "handlingLevel": 0,
      "woundsLevel": 0,
      "crewLevel": -2,
      "passengers": 0,
